    <item>
      <title>美国日益接受加密货币，比特币再次获得提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/bitcoin-btc-gets-another-fillip-from-us-s-growing-embrace-of-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币重新回到了历史最高点附近，这一系列发展凸显了在加密货币支持者唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的领导下，美国对数字资产行业的接受度不断加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/bitcoin-btc-gets-another-fillip-from-us-s-growing-embrace-of-crypto</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 00:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元疲软致油价持稳，创五周多来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走弱且风险偏好情绪席卷整个市场，油价在创下五周多以来的最大涨幅后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 23:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：债券收益率下降，亚洲股市跟随美国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市跟随美国股市上涨，因为美国国债收益率下降有助于增强持有股票的吸引力。交易员们正在密切关注当选总统唐纳德·特朗普计划执政的进一步消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 22:46:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国快递顺丰寻求在香港上市，融资额高达 7.93 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/xiaomi-unit-said-to-invest-in-sf-holding-s-hong-kong-share-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的快递公司顺丰控股有限公司寻求通过香港上市筹集最多 62 亿港元（7.93 亿美元）资金，这是今年香港对大规模股票发行兴趣的又一次测试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/xiaomi-unit-said-to-invest-in-sf-holding-s-hong-kong-share-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 12:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺和诺德在中国推出 Wegovy，价格低于美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/novo-nordisk-launches-wegovy-in-china-with-prices-well-below-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 正在中国推出其最畅销的减肥药 Wegovy，价格仅为美国的一小部分，这是其畅销产品系列打开庞大且快速增长的市场的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/novo-nordisk-launches-wegovy-in-china-with-prices-well-below-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 12:17:06 GMT</pubDate>
